ssly, is .a </div><div class="t mec2 x61 h2d y135b ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">master, and he is a slave, and the repeated act of indul-</div><div class="t m2d1 x61 h2d y1c69 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">gence is intemperance, fraught with the same direful </div><div class="t m31d x61 h2d yc7e ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">consequences, bondage of soul and body, and at last ir-</div><div class="t m862 x64 h2d y1b34 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">retrievable ruin. Thus tobacco in its various forms </div><div class="t m32e x61 h2d yeaa ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">holds millions in its power. Tea and coffee hold mil-</div><div class="t m14db x61 h2d y74c ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lions more in bondage. Of course the last two are not as&apos; </div><div class="t me08 x61 h2d y11e3 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">bad as the use of alcohol, opium, absinthe, and tobacco, </div><div class="t m6a6 x64 h2d y135f ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">but, though milder, they do no good, they enslave the </div><div class="t m12e4 x61 h2d y1078 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mind, blunt the finer sensibilities of the soul, and so un-</div><div class="t m111e x61 h2d y1b90 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fit it to appreciate the glorious truths bf God. Freedom </div><div class="t ma9a x64 h2d y1cd5 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in Christ is freedom from every enthralling habit. </div><div class="t mcc7 xd h2d y1db9 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
